{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/posts/pznqs7","result":{"data":{"sitePage":null},"pageContext":{"url":"posts/pznqs7","relativePath":"posts/pznqs7","frontmatter":{"title":"时钟指针图","stackbit_url_path":"posts/pznqs7","date":"2022-02-25T09:41:18","excerpt":"","tags":[],"categories":[],"template":"post"},"html":"<p>最近在描述一些软件的设计和实现的问题时，想了几种可视化的表达方式，最终发现使用时钟指针图，最能形象化地表达我所遇到的一些问题。</p>\n<p>我目前遇到的问题是，软件的设计本身不合理，然而最终实现，又偏离了这个不合理的设计。</p>\n<p><a name=xRZHz></a></p>\n<h1>南辕北辙</h1>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/221736/1645780951409-a43c46b8-86cf-450b-80c1-a823eb69237e.png#clientId=u56a04109-bce1-4&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=1&#x26;crop=1&#x26;from=paste&#x26;height=517&#x26;id=ud2e5ec0c&#x26;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&#x26;name=image.png&#x26;originHeight=1034&#x26;originWidth=898&#x26;originalType=binary%E2%88%B6=1&#x26;rotation=0&#x26;showTitle=false&#x26;size=53844&#x26;status=done&#x26;style=none&#x26;taskId=u0ca13c7e-4b79-4f3c-b986-15ea62e4a55&#x26;title=&#x26;width=449\" alt=\"image.png\"><br />以上这种情况，导致最终实现与最佳实践完全相悖，即南辕北辙。要稳妥地解决，建议先修 BUG，再做方案调整。<br /><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/221736/1645781382663-bb102cc4-4c0e-401c-98a6-02f8b1d000e8.png#clientId=u56a04109-bce1-4&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=1&#x26;crop=1&#x26;from=paste&#x26;height=450&#x26;id=u3ca0c33b&#x26;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&#x26;name=image.png&#x26;originHeight=900&#x26;originWidth=930&#x26;originalType=binary%E2%88%B6=1&#x26;rotation=0&#x26;showTitle=false&#x26;size=70872&#x26;status=done&#x26;style=none&#x26;taskId=u3878e53c-9509-44b3-8b57-089fc33d8d4&#x26;title=&#x26;width=465\" alt=\"image.png\"></p>\n<p>这样，在描述进度时，可能需要增加第 4 根指针。并不是说表盘上有 4 根指针，只是灰色部分的（实现）指针移动了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/221736/1645783221283-f3307726-525f-4635-a843-7b61204c35b9.png#clientId=u440e036d-78c6-4&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=1&#x26;crop=1&#x26;from=paste&#x26;height=510&#x26;id=u7c4b6543&#x26;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&#x26;name=image.png&#x26;originHeight=1020&#x26;originWidth=988&#x26;originalType=binary%E2%88%B6=1&#x26;rotation=0&#x26;showTitle=false&#x26;size=84141&#x26;status=done&#x26;style=none&#x26;taskId=ud15a334d-ff15-4cfd-b3ea-9fbf9ff46d4&#x26;title=&#x26;width=494\" alt=\"image.png\"></p>\n<p><a name=IvZOy></a></p>\n<h1>歪打正着</h1>\n<p>如果运气好（没见过），可能会有这种情况：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/221736/1645781176859-831a10fb-26f0-4eb2-ac30-6da790b6fbe3.png#clientId=u56a04109-bce1-4&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=1&#x26;crop=1&#x26;from=paste&#x26;height=420&#x26;id=ufc225ddc&#x26;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&#x26;name=image.png&#x26;originHeight=840&#x26;originWidth=924&#x26;originalType=binary%E2%88%B6=1&#x26;rotation=0&#x26;showTitle=false&#x26;size=51767&#x26;status=done&#x26;style=none&#x26;taskId=u7d4e83ec-9ad4-417b-9a9a-1314a7e87c2&#x26;title=&#x26;width=462\" alt=\"image.png\"></p>\n<p>不过，这种歪打正着的情况，我其实没有见过。</p>\n<p>有一些常见的漫画，比如这种：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/221736/1645781812299-68122644-c5bf-40f3-98ce-9fcf269f3835.png#clientId=u56a04109-bce1-4&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=1&#x26;crop=1&#x26;from=paste&#x26;height=514&#x26;id=u025ffce0&#x26;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&#x26;name=image.png&#x26;originHeight=1027&#x26;originWidth=1666&#x26;originalType=binary%E2%88%B6=1&#x26;rotation=0&#x26;showTitle=false&#x26;size=1265676&#x26;status=done&#x26;style=none&#x26;taskId=u75de82a2-c93e-4187-a739-b3c4f3b02a2&#x26;title=&#x26;width=833\" alt=\"image.png\"><br />其实也可以使用时钟指针图来描述，即：</p>\n<p><a name=UaMxj></a></p>\n<h1>秋千漫画的时钟指针表示</h1>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/221736/1645782044357-562a4f5b-dece-438f-992c-8f3527dfa039.png#clientId=u56a04109-bce1-4&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=1&#x26;crop=1&#x26;from=paste&#x26;height=606&#x26;id=udf463c69&#x26;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&#x26;name=image.png&#x26;originHeight=1212&#x26;originWidth=1038&#x26;originalType=binary%E2%88%B